<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Declaration Adopted at Uruguay Round Meeting </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Conference Formally Adopts Declaration </H4>

<F P=102> NC1504105794 Paris AFP in English 1037 GMT 15 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC1504105794 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AFP </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Marrakesh, Morocco, April 15 (AFP)--The GATT 
ministerial conference formally adopted the Marrakesh 
Declaration on Friday [15 April], formally endorsing the outcome 
of the Uruguay Round trade negotiations. 

</TEXT>

