developments in Yemen, which is going through a passing crisis, 
God willing, and the national efforts being currently made at 
the level of dialogues in order to emerge from the crisis. We 
appreciate every effort, including Maghreban efforts that were 
demonstrated in the Tunis conference and the efforts made by 
President Zine El Abidine to support the Yemeni cause. [passage 
omitted] [end recording] 

