<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-NES-94-073 </AU>
Daily Report 
<DATE1>  15 Apr 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> Iran </F>
<H3> <TI>   Habibi Calls For Khuzestan Development Organization </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Habibi Calls For Khuzestan Development Organization </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1504060994 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
First Program Network in Persian 0330 GMT 15 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1504060994 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran 
First Program Network </F>

<F P=105>  Persian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The first vice president has called for a regional 
development organization in Khuzestan. Habibi, who attended the 
Khuzestan Province Administrative Council session last night, 
said that in view of the favorable circumstances in Khuzestan, 
this organization can accelerate the area's growth and progress. 
  Various provincial officials briefed the session on the 
developments and problems of Khuzestan. The ministers of 
agriculture and of culture and Islamic guidance attended last 
night's session. 

</TEXT>

