<F P=100> ARAB AFRICA </F>
<F P=101> Algeria </F>
<H3> <TI>   Presidency Spokesman Announces New Algerian Government </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Presidency Spokesman Announces New Algerian Government </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1504201794 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1900 
GMT 15 Apr 94 </F>

