charge of military security]. Thank you. [end recording] 
  The new ministers will be installed at their ministeries 
tomorrow at ceremonies to be attended by the prime minister. 
After the ceremonies they will begin their new duties. Details 
on the new figures making up the new government will be given 
tomorrow. 

