<F P=100> Palestinian Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Collaborators Receive Israeli Identity Cards </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Collaborators Receive Israeli Identity Cards </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA1804072794 Jerusalem AL-NAHAR in Arabic 14 Apr 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> TA1804072794 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem AL-NAHAR </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] In recent weeks, scores of collaborators with 
Israel have received blue Israeli identity cards. This came 
after the PLO, in its negotiations with Israel, refused to issue 
a general amnesty for collaborators. 
  This identity card permits collaborators and their families 
to live wherever they wish in Israel. A large number of 
collaborators have expressed their intention to reside in Arab 
villages within the Green Line. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

