Arabs'"] 
  [Excerpt] Islamabad-London, AL-SHARQ AL-AWSAT -- [Passage 
omitted] The leader of a major Afghan faction, who asked to 
remain anonymous, has said that the majority of Arab volunteers 
in the Afghan jihad, known as the Afghan Arabs, are in 
Afghanistan, and that camps have been opened to retrain and 
