and forces in the Arab region. Asked about the faction 
sponsoring, training, and rehabilitating these Afghan Arabs, the 
Afghan leader said that all the major Afghan factions have such 
camps, and that the Arab region will witness new waves of 
violence unless conditions in Afghanistan calm down and one 
central authority is established. [passage omitted] 

