<H3> <TI>   Bhutto Leaves Lahore on 4-Day Visit to Germany </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Bhutto Leaves Lahore on 4-Day Visit to Germany </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK1804082894 Islamabad Radio Pakistan Overseas Service in 
