<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    SLA `Massacre' in 'Aramta Village Reported </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC1604083894 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 0800 GMT 16 Apr 
94 </F>

<F P=103> NC1604083894 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Agent Lahd's militia elements [South Lebanese 
Army--SLA] entered the village of 'Aramta this morning to commit 
a massacre. They killed citizen Jihad Jahjah on the road and 
assassinated citizen Fu'ad Jandal Yunus in his home. They also 
wounded Warrant Officer Nabil al-Haj and a woman named 
Umm-Sulayman. The agents evicted the village's inhabitants to 
Jazzin. 

</TEXT>

