Ukrainian Foreign Minister Mr. [Anatoliy] Zlenko. During this 
meeting, the Ukrainian foreign minister handed over a message 
from Ukrainian President Leonid Kravchuk and said: Since 
independence, Ukraine has been willing to expand cooperation 
with the great country of Iran in all fields of mutual 
