from his Ukrainian counterpart and expressed satisfaction for 
the promotion of ties between the two countries. He said: We 
believe our bilateral cooperation can be expanded beyond its 
present level, and thanks to the two countries' officials, the 
existing level of cooperation, which will serve the interests of 
the two countries and the world, should be further accelerated. 
  In his message, the Ukrainian president renewed his 
invitation to Mr. Hashemi-Rafsanjani to visit that country. 

