performed operations during the ceremonies. 
  Also present at the ceremomies were Chief of Staff of Armed 
Forces Brigadier General Hasan Firuzabadi, Army Chief of Staff 
Major General 'Ali Shahbazi and a number of other senior army 
officials. 

