<H3> <TI>   RCD To Boycott Transitional National Council </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    RCD To Boycott Transitional National Council </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1704203094 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1900 
GMT 17 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1704203094 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers ENTV Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Concerning the setting up of the Transitional 
National Council, debates on whether to take part in it have 
flavored the lives of political parties. 
  After the National Liberation Front, the Socialist Forces 
Front, Ennahda, Ettahadi Movement, and the Democratic Movement 
for the Renewal of Algeria announced they were boycotting the 
council, the Rally for Culture and Democracy announced that it 
would not be participating. The Algerian People's Union, 
however, has agreed to join in. 

</TEXT>

