<F P=103> LD1704165294 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers ENTV Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] Mr. Belkacem Abadli, a central inspector at the 
Ministry of Religious Affairs, has been assassinated. The 
victim, who was born in 1945, was married and had five children. 
He was abducted from his home in Larba on 13 April and found 
dead in Sidi Moussa yesterday. 
  The deceased will be buried tomorrow at El Tar, his place of 
birth. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

