<F P=106> [Unattributed report: "Two Diplomats Admit Assassinating </F>
Iraqi Oppositionist"] 
  [Excerpt] Beirut, Paris, London, AL-SHARQ AL-AWSAT -- An 
authoritative Lebanese source has said that the two Iraqi 
attaches detained on charges of assassinating Iraqi 
oppositionist Shaykh Talib Suhayl al-Tamimi in Beirut yesterday 
admitted killing the person in question on orders from Iraqi 
